Package org.vulcanium

Interface RegionAccessor

All Known Subinterfaces:
LimitedRegion, World
public interface RegionAccessor
A RegionAccessor gives access to getting, modifying, and spawning Biome, BlockState, and Entity, as well as generating basic structures.
